<title type="html"><![CDATA[6/9(Thu) Dragon Boat Festival/ 18 Ways To Get Better At Working Under Pressure (Host: Alan)]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/viewtopic.php?t=624&amp;p=647#p647"><![CDATA[
6/9 (Thu) Dragon Boat Festival/ 18 Ways To Get Better At Working Under Pressure (Host: Alan)<br /><br />Agenda:<br />7:00-7:05 pm Opening Remarks<br />7:05-7:40 pm Session 1: Group Discussion<br />7:40-8:00 pm Individual Presentation<br />8:00-8:05 pm Break<br />8:05-8:40: Session 2: Group Discussion<br />8:40-9:00 pm Individual Presentation<br /><br />We will hold a zoom meeting only.<br /><br />Zoom meeting: Please click the link below<br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://zoomtw.zoom.us/j/92987266213?pw">https://zoomtw.zoom.us/j/92987266213?pw</a><!-- m --> ...<br />Meeting ID:929 8726 6213<br />Password:112233<br /><br />Session I<br />Dragon Boat Festival<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.travelking.com.tw/eng/tourguide/taiwanfestivals/dragonboat-festival.asp">https://www.travelking.com.tw/eng/tourg ... stival.asp</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Questions<br />1. Why do we call it Dragon Boat Festival?<br />2. What food is eaten on the Dragon Boat Festival?<br />3. What are the customs of the Dragon Boat Festival?<br />4. What sport is most popular during Dragon Boat Festival?<br /><br /><br /><br />Session II<br />18 Ways To Get Better At Working Under Pressure<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.forbes.com/sites/forbescoachescouncil/2017/07/28/18-ways-to-get-better-at-working-under-pressure/?sh=6aecce2e3597">https://www.forbes.com/sites/forbescoac ... ecce2e3597</a><!-- m --><br /><br /><br />Additional Pack for Reference<br /><br />1.5 Ways to Reduce Stress<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MPPMgz4zZ0w&amp;list=TLPQMTUwNTIwMjJoh1YHSTGsFg&amp;index=5">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MPPMgz4 ... Fg&amp;index=5</a><!-- m --><br />&quot;Within each setback and obstacle there is a seed of an equal or greater advantage or benefit. Find it&quot;<br /><br />2.How to make stress your friend<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RcGyVTAoXEU">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RcGyVTAoXEU</a><!-- m --><br /><br /><br />Questions<br />1.What is always stressing you out?<br />2.How do you rid yourself of stress?<br />3.Do you think stress will lead to medical problems?<br />4.How do you communicate about stress with your significant others or friends?<br /><br /><br />P.S.<br />1.參加三次(含實體及線上會議)後，只要繳交1,000元(學生500元)，即可成為ROYAL終身會員!<br />2.請帶著開放的心與熱情來參加全英文會話聚會!<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=38674">Louie Wang</a> — Sat Jun 04, 2022 8:17 pm</p><hr />
